title: Prince Lionheart POP Wipe Warmer, Pink
features: Use with patented ever fresh system
Keeps wipes moist and fresh, non browning
description: Changing diapers doesn't have to be a shocking experience for baby with the Prince Lionheart Wipes Warmer Pop. Available in your choice of color, this Wipes Warmer is not only fun, but is also made to protect your baby's delicate skin. Designed with the patented Ever-Fresh System, this wipes warmer keeps your wipes fresh and moist and will not discolor. An Ever-Fresh Pillow keeps your wipes moist with micropores which traps and releases water as needed and prevents discoloration by insulating your wipes from the warming system. A pop-up lid allows for safer, one-handed dispensing. Warmed to the perfect temperature, you and your baby will appreciate this wipes warmer! About Prince Lionheart: Prince Lionheart is a family-owned and operated business that began in the family's garage in 1973, with long hours crafting handmade rocking horses and a commitment to quality, innovation and outstanding service. Though the garage has since been replaced by a state-of-the-art manufacturing facility in Santa Maria, California, the core values and high quality standards of the family business have never changed. Features patented Ever-Fresh System.
